<c.bg_transparent>Los saltamontes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y las frambuesas tampoco son venenosos.</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:08:11.282 --> 00:08:12.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es una mazmorra de verdad.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:08:13.576 --> 00:08:15.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nunca había visto una.</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:08:17.371 --> 00:08:20.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Hay magia estancada aquí,
y el aire está quieto.</i></c.bg_transparent>

109
00:08:20.333 --> 00:08:22.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Es una cueva formada naturalmente.</i></c.bg_transparent>

110
00:08:24.378 --> 00:08:25.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Oye, es peligroso!</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:08:31.260 --> 00:08:32.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No te preocupes.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:08:32.887 --> 00:08:34.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vengo aquí a menudo.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:08:34.430 --> 00:08:36.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estarás a salvo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>si te quedas en el suelo seco.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:08:57.036 --> 00:08:58.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vaya.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:08:58.996 --> 00:09:02.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Las mazmorras están repletas de espíritus.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:09:05.127 --> 00:09:08.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tomé tierra y agua de aquí,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y las puse dentro de mi frasco.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:09:09.924 --> 00:09:11.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya veo.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:09:11.968 --> 00:09:14.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué sueles hacer cuando vienes aquí?</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:09:15.805 --> 00:09:18.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Escribo cartas y leo libros.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:09:19.225 --> 00:09:22.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Así que esto es el resultado
de su holgazanería.</i></c.bg_transparent>

121
00:09:25.439 --> 00:09:28.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Como sea,
este lugar parece bastante seguro.</i></c.bg_transparent>

122
00:09:29.819 --> 00:09:30.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Espera.</i></c.bg_transparent>

123
00:09:31.320 --> 00:09:34.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Si cultivo este lugar
y siembro mandrágoras,</i></c.bg_transparent>

124
00:09:34.407 --> 00:09:37.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>podré usar la magia
de la mazmorra con seguridad.</i></c.bg_transparent>

125
00:09:38.286 --> 00:09:40.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Sí, debería funcionar.</i></c.bg_transparent>

126
00:09:40.162 --> 00:09:42.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>También está
a una buena distancia del agua.</i></c.bg_transparent>

127
00:09:46.043 --> 00:09:48.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Una baba!</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:09:48.254 --> 00:09:51.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Deberíamos quemar a todos los monstruos!</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:09:51.173 --> 00:09:52.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No!</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:09:55.720 --> 00:09:57.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué hiciste eso?</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:09:59.599 --> 00:10:02.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No se avanzará</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>en un área iluminada por el sol.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:10:07.106 --> 00:10:11.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>La baba descompone el excremento</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de murciélago y lo convierte en magia.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:10:12.987 --> 00:10:16.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sin ellas, la mazmorra desaparecerá.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:10:19.619 --> 00:10:20.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Murciélagos…</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:10:21.579 --> 00:10:22.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Toma.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:10:35.468 --> 00:10:36.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Están buenas.</i></c.bg_transparent>

137
00:10:37.511 --> 00:10:41.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Si saben tan bien,
seguro otros animales también las comen.</i></c.bg_transparent>

138
00:10:43.225 --> 00:10:46.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Me pregunto
qué comen los murciélagos aquí.</i></c.bg_transparent>

139
00:10:47.355 --> 00:10:49.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>¿Cuándo dan frutos estos frambuesos?</i></c.bg_transparent>

140
00:10:50.066 --> 00:10:52.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>¿Qué animales comen frambuesas?</i></c.bg_transparent>

141
00:10:53.402 --> 00:10:57.073 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Sin saber eso,
no podré diseñar una mazmorra.</i></c.bg_transparent>

142
00:11:01.077 --> 00:11:03.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Hay mucho que no sé.</i></c.bg_transparent>

143
00:11:08.084 --> 00:11:09.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Gracias por traerme aquí.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:11:11.504 --> 00:11:15.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Creí que solo debía estudiar magia</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para mejorar.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:11:16.509 --> 00:11:18.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero parece que me equivoqué.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:11:22.014 --> 00:11:23.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por cierto,</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:11:23.766 --> 00:11:27.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>soy Falin. ¿Cómo te llamas?</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:11:35.444 --> 00:11:37.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Marcille.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:11:37.363 --> 00:11:40.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Falin, me encantaría ser tu amiga.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:11:42.910 --> 00:11:45.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿La estudiante más brillante</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>en la historia de la escuela?</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:11:45.246 --> 00:11:46.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eso tiene que ser falso.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:11:46.664 --> 00:11:48.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Es cierto!</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:11:48.290 --> 00:11:50.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>En la escuela,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>yo era una estudiante excelente.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:11:52.128 --> 00:11:55.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>En fin, esta mazmorra</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>es un lugar alucinante.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:11:56.632 --> 00:11:58.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Está perfectamente calculada,</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:11:58.926 --> 00:12:01.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>y aquí circulan continuamente</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>cantidades enormes de magia.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:12:01.971 --> 00:12:05.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si este mago lunático realmente existe,</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:12:05.224 --> 00:12:07.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>definitivamente no está cuerdo.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:12:08.436 --> 00:12:11.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Senshi, lo mejor sería</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que buscaras otro lugar donde vivir.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:12:12.523 --> 00:12:13.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eso no te incumbe.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:12:14.567 --> 00:12:16.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>En primer lugar, odias la magia,</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:12:16.819 --> 00:12:19.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡pero esta mazmorra</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>está construida con magia!</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:12:20.906 --> 00:12:22.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No te oigo.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:12:23.492 --> 00:12:24.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya veo.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:12:24.785 --> 00:12:26.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Así que hablaba de ti.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:12:28.038 --> 00:12:31.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuando mi hermana</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>se inscribió en la escuela de magia,</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:12:32.001 --> 00:12:34.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>las cartas que me enviaba</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>estaban llenas de preocupación.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:12:35.504 --> 00:12:38.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Pero, desde que me dijo
que había hecho una amiga,</i></c.bg_transparent>

169
00:12:38.757 --> 00:12:41.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>parecía que disfrutaba cada día.</i></c.bg_transparent>

170
00:12:43.387 --> 00:12:45.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Decía que eras una persona increíble.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:12:46.307 --> 00:12:47.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Siempre te elogiaba.</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:12:53.606 --> 00:12:55.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A ti también te elogiaba.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:12:55.900 --> 00:12:57.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Decía que te respetaba.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:12:58.486 --> 00:12:59.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Eso decía?</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:13:01.906 --> 00:13:03.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿En qué es bueno?</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:13:03.199 --> 00:13:05.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es muy bueno imitando a un perro.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:13:07.161 --> 00:13:11.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Bueno, supongo
que no es momento de lloriquear.</i></c.bg_transparent>

178
00:13:11.207 --> 00:13:12.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Muy bien.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:13:12.249 --> 00:13:15.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Rescatemos a Falin lo antes posible!</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:13:16.670 --> 00:13:18.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Vamos!</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:13:18.547 --> 00:13:21.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Si estás despierto, levántate!</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:13:22.885 --> 00:13:24.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aquí estamos ahora.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:13:25.012 --> 00:13:28.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Según los orcos, este es el lugar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>donde se vio al dragón rojo.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:13:28.724 --> 00:13:30.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estamos a unos dos días de allí.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:13:31.018 --> 00:13:33.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es probable que el dragón</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>no se quede en un lugar,</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:13:33.437 --> 00:13:36.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>pero tampoco es un monstruo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que deambule por ahí.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:13:37.107 --> 00:13:39.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo ideal sería acampar dos veces más.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:13:39.693 --> 00:13:41.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Una vez a la mitad</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:13:41.570 --> 00:13:43.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y otra vez antes de llegar al dragón rojo.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:13:43.989 --> 00:13:47.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sacaremos a Laios de la cama</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>cuando se consuma la vela.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:13:47.326 --> 00:13:49.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Asegúrense de estar listos.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:13:49.161 --> 00:13:51.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nuestro próximo descanso</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>será un poco lejos.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:13:53.582 --> 00:13:55.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quiero limpiarme.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:13:56.460 --> 00:13:57.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Dónde?</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:13:57.795 --> 00:13:59.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>En el rincón de la habitación.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:14:00.798 --> 00:14:02.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Que sea rápido.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:14:06.637 --> 00:14:08.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esperaremos afuera.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:14:08.931 --> 00:14:10.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pueden quedarse aquí.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:14:11.058 --> 00:14:12.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Puedo hacerlo vestida.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:14:14.395 --> 00:14:15.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si tú lo dices…</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:14:18.065 --> 00:14:19.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Los estoy molestando, ¿no?</i></c.bg_transparent>

202
00:14:20.568 --> 00:14:24.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tal vez debería haber estudiado
magia de ilusiones.</i></c.bg_transparent>

203
00:14:24.363 --> 00:14:26.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Pero ese no es el problema, ¿no?</i></c.bg_transparent>

204
00:14:26.699 --> 00:14:29.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Era más fácil
cuando la mitad éramos chicas.</i></c.bg_transparent>

205
00:14:30.536 --> 00:14:32.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Aquí nos separamos.</i></c.bg_transparent>

206
00:14:33.080 --> 00:14:35.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué? ¿De verdad tienen que irse ahora?</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:39.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aún no sabemos qué le pasó a Falin.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:14:40.838 --> 00:14:44.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo siento, pero también</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tenemos que ganarnos la vida.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:14:45.843 --> 00:14:48.596 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>De solo pensarlo me pongo mal.</i></c.bg_transparent>

210
00:14:48.679 --> 00:14:50.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Y pensé que eran nuestros amigos.</i></c.bg_transparent>

211
00:14:55.644 --> 00:14:57.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Levántate, Laios!</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:14:57.187 --> 00:14:58.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Oye, despierta!</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:14:58.856 --> 00:15:00.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
